			<h2><br/>Open source is a better way</h2>
			<img src="assets/osdc-idea.png" width="300" height="300" align="left">
			<ul><br />
				<li class="fragment">Transparency → accountability</li>
				<li class="fragment">Collaboration → innovative ideas</li>
				<li class="fragment">Rapid prototyping → failing faster</li>
				<li class="fragment">Meritocracy → best ideas, buy-in</li>
				<li class="fragment">Passion → commitment</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
